the search pattern.
NIL means case sensitive search will be forced."
  :type '(choice (const :tag "Case Fold Search" case-fold-search)
                 (const :tag "Smart" smart)
                 (const :tag "Force" force)
                 (const :tag "Off" nil))
  :group 'rg)

